{"tid":2515860,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度人染疫連累重慶食肆生意大跌9成 「淡到離晒譜」","createTime":"2021-05-04T09:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T09:43:13.000Z","uid":38539,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a6610b5e8dd1e09c99a5abb15319230d59dbbdde","tid":2515860,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:17:03.000Z","msg":"染變種病毒的東涌映灣園菲傭牽一髮動全身，港府勒令全港37萬外傭須在本月9日前進行強制檢測，令全港外傭在過去周六日，被迫捨棄假期的休息時間，在檢測站日曬雨淋，大排長龍輪候作檢測。而杜拜來港住佐敦的印裔男及其女友的確診個案，令港人對印度餐廳望而卻步，印度食肆生意大跌九成，老闆叫苦連天。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQMwpngnSGfdTE6AFG7nULoTVoDKk2NQa3J7LJvCgvK9z?filename=HctmjzT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHctmjzT.jpg&h=5a4faaf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尖沙嘴重慶大廈是印巴裔人士集中之地，《蘋果》今日到場採訪，店舖、食肆雖有開門，但人流冷清，門堪羅雀。居港53年的印度人Bob，他說剛在上周做了病毒檢測，他認為是需要的，每人都應該做（檢測）。他覺得進行檢測並無問題，亦不擔心變種病毒在其少數族裔群組廣傳。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPzEG9ZPB1gUSTHhzjCLvqw2oivMRQibZ63UG64AYfD3W?filename=yRXuttx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyRXuttx.jpg&h=e00b95ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過，在重慶大廈內開餐廳的Jacky，則埋怨印度人確診新聞報道一出，對其生意影響極大。「呢個印度人中招，就驚第二個印度人會否都有病，呢兩個星期生意額跌咗99%，一日得兩、三枱客，你話死唔死，係禮拜五、六、日先好啲，放假出嚟食吓飯，禮拜一至四完全冇生意，好淡，淡到離晒譜！新聞一出，個個都驚，香港人最驚呢啲嘢，起碼一個月冇生意，啲人要睇吓21日之內重慶有冇事發生。」他指政府不應「搞大件事」，「唔好嚇到人個個都驚晒，香港係好地方，唔好搞到人哋個個都驚，唔好搞大件事，生意影響好大，跌咗90至99%。」他又說人人戴口罩不怕傳染，談到印度疫情失控，他說「啲人唔聽政府講，幾百萬人去選舉，坐埋一堆，一定有影響，集體傳染。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPUbenKwXdLU14YyviZCtHE5C9wn6tkL1camL1qh4MRr3?filename=Gu13xUZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGu13xUZ.jpg&h=f1a85f53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfXT8Ex1GSHHHs7KgqSMQNaGyXGeNGzH3W56UtB29Arsc?filename=PhesZz5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPhesZz5.jpg&h=f7e25b4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcowhC2S7dCQ3Urampr1yHyjyCiab55JwbEErNwT3XSNW?filename=4u2Y6e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4u2Y6e5.jpg&h=05ca9057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTmuui2oqVGE5jdZqm51eQRhmfvVTpGrfFhrh9pJz7Vsq?filename=aYnm31K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaYnm31K.jpg&h=5e29b026&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210504/EFN4R2HTLFFQZCBGTD5AHY2HSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210504%2FEFN4R2HTLFFQZCBGTD5AHY2HSA%2F&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnvZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=928683a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210504%2FEFN4R2HTLFFQZCBGTD5AHY2HSA%2F&h=33a28afd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210504/EFN4R2HTLFFQZCBGTD5AHY2HSA/</a>"},{"pid":"9ce99dee330f5a76808b97522ee2391b108a6cb8","tid":2515860,"uid":36481,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:19:52.000Z","msg":"點解政府唔叫重慶大廈啲人強檢<br />\n菲傭就要<br />\n係咪想挑起亞洲列強大戰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70524dedb1d09aef4fc01abf0c322bf69bbb5545","tid":2515860,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9ce99dee330f5a76808b97522ee2391b108a6cb8","tid":2515860,"uid":36481,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:19:52.000Z","msg":"點解政府唔叫重慶大廈啲人強檢<br />\n菲傭就要<br />\n係咪想挑起亞洲列強大戰<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:32:40.000Z","msg":"因為已經強檢咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上個禮拜"},{"pid":"742361649d65c63dfd49abd1621301a51553e8e0","tid":2515860,"uid":206354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T09:35:31.000Z","msg":"唔好搞大件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcf19fd9bfac833c836d805d11da27e9c2290b55","tid":2515860,"uid":38